  "reviews": "\u201cOne Finger Death Punch is the greatest two-button kung fu game ever made. And its sequel is even better.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-04-17-one-finger-death-punch-is-the-greatest-two-button-kung-fu-game-ever-made\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >EUROGAMER</a><br><br>\u201cOne Finger Death Punch 2 manages to take a simplistic gameplay system and turn it into one of the most bizarrely addictive score chasers I've ever played.\u201d<br>9.5/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://techraptor.net/content/one-finger-death-punch-2-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >TechRaptor</a><br><br>\u201cIt\u2019s simplistic, yet utterly exhilarating!\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://One Finger Death Punch 2 manages to take a simplistic gameplay system and turn it into one of the most bizarrely addictive score chasers I've ever played.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >One Finger Death Punch 2 manages to take a simplistic gameplay system and turn it into one of the most bizarrely addictive score chasers I've ever played.</a><br>",
